│ SCEV computation that eventually calls collectFromPHI again, creating infinite recursion.                                                                        │
│                                                                                                                                                                  │
│ 4. Proposed Edit Point(s): Add a recursion depth limit check at the beginning of collectFromPHI to prevent excessive recursion. The function already has a Depth │
│ parameter that is incremented when making recursive calls, but it's not being used to limit recursion. Adding a reasonable depth limit (e.g., 32) will prevent   │
│ infinite recursion while still allowing legitimate deep analyses.                                                                                                │
